mcbenchmark

Description
------------


This is a benchmark tool for memcached, which used the library libmemcached.
The program based on the tool redis-benchmark and the different implementations
like http://www.github.com/idning/mc-benchmark and
http://www.github.com/antirez/mc-benchmark.

Installation
--------------

See in the INSTALL file for the concrete install instruction.

Usage
------

Run the tool with the options -h or --help to see the usage instraction of the
program.

